Author: red_ossifrage
Text: Yikes, I'm so sorry you had that experience in childhood.

Author: personne-inconnue
Text: I feel like this a lot but I think it stems from being invalidated all the time growing up. My parents never believed I was sick, tired, depressed, socially anxious - they just said it was all made up or that I was exaggerating. Now I doubt and second guess myself and my feelings at every chance. sorry for the ramble.
